Tanzanite One Names Ed Nealon Chairman, Farai Manyemba as Finance Director

-- B y   J o h n   V i l j o e n
-- 
2011-06-27T06:06:05Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-27/tanzanite-one-names-ed-nealon-chairman-farai-manyemba-as-finance-director.html
Tanzanite One Ltd. (TNZ)  said Ed Nealon
will assume the role of non-executive chairman and Ami Mpungwe
will become non-executive deputy chairman. Farai Manyemba is
appointed finance director, the company said in a statement
today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
John Viljoen at 
 jviljoen@bloomberg.net  